	"system": {
		"description": "<p><em>Passive: You can fall up to 30 feet without taking falling damage. You also gain proficiency in Acrobatics or Performance (your choice).</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Meteoric Momentum:</strong> When you move at least 20 feet in a straight line before making a melee weapon attack, you can expend a Legend Die to increase your speed. For 1 minute, your speed is increased by 5ft. You can stack speed increases if you use Meteoric Momentum again. Additionally, you can Dash as a bonus action during the turn you activate this legend dice feature.</p>",
